                <h1>Who Owns Progressive Insurance? Insights & Overview</h1>
                <p>Progressive Insurance is owned by Progressive Corporation, which was founded in 1937 by Joseph Lewis and Peter Lewis. It's a publicly traded company, meaning shares are held by investors and shareholders. The company has grown to be one of the largest auto insurance providers in the U.S., known for its innovative approaches to insurance.</p>
